://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.7508433118242563, \"rank\": 0.3316974798856012, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jamaica\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 251}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 4x100-meter relay\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Athletics Championships\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Athletics Centre\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP Three-time Olympic gold medalist sprinter Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce of Jamaica has announced that she will retire after participating in the Olympic Games in Paris this year and explained her decision to Essence.com in an interview.\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shelly-Ann_Fraser-Pryce\"}, {\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999996152956386, \"rank\": 3.420355615946671e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999559238414, \"rank\": 4.407622415161934e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essence_(magazine)\", \"score\": 0.9988159927504948, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Essence.com\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essence_(magazine)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Essence_(magazine)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 608}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is not a day I am getting up to go practice and I am like, 'I am over this,'\\\" Fraser-Pryce said.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a day\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"Fraser-Pryce\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My son needs me.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My son\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My husband and I have been together since before I won in 2008.\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My husband\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has sacrificed for me.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are a partnership, a team.\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a partnership\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's because of that support that I am able to do the things that I have been doing for all these years.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that support\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"the things\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 949}, {\"ngram\": \"all these years\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think I now owe it to them to do something else.\\\"\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having made her Olympic debut in 2008 in Beijing, Fraser-Pryce won eight medals, including three golds, four silvers and one bronze in the women's 100-meter, 200-meter and 4x100-meter relay events in Beijing, London, Rio de Janeiro and Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.2991770991211546e-12, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 3.2991770991211546e-12, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9993317996568811, \"rank\": 0.000668183984048738, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1268, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.4282816237758356e-12, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1287, \"end\": 1292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999272600848157, \"rank\": 7.274520531004178e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_20